data.description: 3750 Sq Ft of living space. 4 BR 3 BA downstairs plus bonus room and full bath upstairs. Energy efficient with spray foam insulation and tankless water heater. Open floor plan with large kitchen. Double oven and gas stove. Walk in pantry. AirPlay surround sound and smart alarm system. Fully landscaped yard with irrigation and privacy fence. Covered back patio.
data.whatILove: Quiet gated community in Pike Road. Walking trail with 3 ponds in main area. Convenient to Pike Road school and Eastchase.
